I swear to God on my life that this serial does NOT work!  Dont waste your time.  When you try to "apply changes" it first calls home to verify the serial with a registration server and all these serials I have tried are all BLACKLISTED.  

I even tried editing my hosts file to ban access to the ip it was using to call home but when I did that it just called home to a different ip address (They have multiple registration servers apparently).  i WASTED 30 MINUTES ON THIS CRAP AND AM NOW GIVING UP.  

I hope the programmers get anal cancer and die a slow death.  Bastards!!
